600.subject: ENDO
600.courseDescription: Current Literature Review I. (1-0). Credit 1. Detailed review of recently published literature on all subjects related to endodontics; critical evaluation of the scientific literature; student assignment of recent issues of 28 selected dental journals for critical review of pertinent articles for scientific merit and clinical relevance. Students register for a total of 9 credit hours.
